00:02:59.659 --> 00:03:03.049
the ones that occurred in India, in the late
19th century.

00:03:03.049 --> 00:03:07.310
India was Britain's most populous and most
important colony in the 19th century and also

00:03:07.310 --> 00:03:11.379
the scene of it's greatest colonial failure,
