00:03:15.310 --> 00:03:21.170
of lives and they highlight the devastating
combination of market forces, government policy,

00:03:21.170 --> 00:03:22.859
ideology, and bad weather.

00:03:22.859 --> 00:03:27.269
Now, it's tempting to blame those devastating
famines on the severe El Niño events that

00:03:27.269 --> 00:03:31.599
occurred in those years, but it's important
to note that there have been El Niños that

00:03:31.599 --> 00:03:36.030
didn't result in famine and also famines that
aren't related to El Niño.

00:03:36.030 --> 00:03:39.049
When studying history - and also when doing
