00:03:44.849 --> 00:03:49.010
that urge to find the one true problem, because
then maybe we could find a one true solution

00:03:49.010 --> 00:03:52.999
but it just doesn't work that way. The truth
is always nuanced.

00:03:52.999 --> 00:03:58.180
Okay, so until about 1800, India was the world's
