the labor intensive Indian textile industry

00:04:19.180 --> 00:04:24.280
couldn't compete. So, former Indian textile
workers turned to growing cotton for export

00:04:24.280 --> 00:04:29.330
which required land, seed and fertilizer,
which cost money. And that drove many Indian

00:04:29.330 --> 00:04:31.190
cotton farmers into debt.

00:04:31.190 --> 00:04:34.099
