00:04:48.449 --> 00:04:53.430
Now, to service that debt, and pay all of those
taxes with money, Indian farmers needed a

00:04:53.430 --> 00:05:00.400
cash crop which meant yet more land devoted
to cotton and less land devoted to growing food.

00:05:00.449 --> 00:05:05.389
During the 1876 to 1878 El Niño drought,
British administrators continued to collect

00:05:05.389 --> 00:05:10.240
